data.description: Such a nice property with an extra lot to the North making the property apprx 120x120! Oversized heated + cooled 2 car garage with extra storage space. Nice deck off the back. Inside features all new windows throughout in 2022, 2BRs on the main floor + 1 room that was converted into a laundry room but could be utilized as a bedroom. All the ductwork was redone in 2017! Basement is unfinished but great storage! Nice covered front porch. All appliances included! Call your Realtor for a showing!
